x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Megan-Thee-Stallion-performing-live-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Megan-Thee-Stallion-performing-live-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Megan-Thee-Stallion-performing-live-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/megan-thee-stallion">梅根·西·斯塔林 (Megan Thee Stallion)</a>公布了她的新单曲《Cobra》的详细信息，该单曲将于下周发行。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/megan-thee-stallion-cover-interview-2020-girls-in-the-hood-2700621">封面——Megan Thee Stallion：</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/megan-thee-stallion-cover-interview-2020-girls-in-the-hood-2700621">“我现在正在为我的王朝而努力”</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>梅根于本周五（10 月 27 日）公布了这首新歌的细节，这是自针对她的前唱片公司的诉讼和解以来的第一首单曲。</p><p>这位说唱歌手本月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-settles-legal-dispute-with-former-record-label-3518761">终于与前厂牌 1501 Certified Entertainment 分道扬镳</a>，她与该公司进行了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-say-her-record-label-is-preventing-release-of-new-music-2619177">长达四年的漫长法律斗争</a>。结果，她还宣布她的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-says-she-has-no-label-and-her-next-album-will-be-self-funded-3515034">新专辑将完全自筹资金</a>：“预算来自我，他妈的 Hot Girl Productions。”</p><p>据新闻稿称，《Cobra》将是“梅根的独立音乐和娱乐实体 Hot Girl Productions 发行的第一首单曲”。</p><p>除了即将发行的单曲的消息外，梅根还发布了单曲的艺术作品。新歌将于 11 月 3 日发布 - 请在此处查看公告： </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Cy6L-Exxt1A/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div styl